creek getting water.

777
00:43:15,059 --> 00:43:16,327
I don't think so.

778
00:43:17,930 --> 00:43:20,935
It's a beautiful night
and a beautiful morning.

779
00:43:22,071 --> 00:43:23,405
Did you see the sunrise?

780
00:43:28,512 --> 00:43:30,747
It's a beautiful
morning, isn't it?

781
00:43:30,781 --> 00:43:32,449
