Let's go.

791
00:43:52,739 --> 00:43:55,241
I don't know why I assumed
you were more open-minded.

792
00:43:55,275 --> 00:43:58,144
Well, I'm not. I
understand the temptation,

793
00:43:58,178 --> 00:44:00,112
