- He needs his mother.

796
00:44:06,153 --> 00:44:08,422
I'm sorry, but you
don't get to do this!

797
00:44:08,455 --> 00:44:10,523
Goodbye, Daddy.

798
00:44:13,160 --> 00:44:16,029
